<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>LIME Computation Results</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .results-table {
            width: 40%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .results-table th, .results-table td {
            border: 1px solid black;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Dear LIME user,</p>

    <p>We have successfully completed the line driven stellar wind computation. Below are the results:</p>

    <h2>Stellar Parameters</h2>
    <table class="results-table">
        <tr><th>Parameter [Unit]</th><th>Value</th></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Luminosity [L<sub>⊙</sub>]</strong></td><td>{{ luminosity }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Effective Temperature [K]</strong></td><td>{{ teff }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Stellar Mass [M<sub>⊙</sub>]</strong></td><td>{{ mstar }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Z<sub>scale</sub></strong></td><td>{{ zscale }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Z<sub>⋆</sub></strong></td><td>{{ zstar }}</td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Computed Line-driven wind Parameters</h2>
    <table class="results-table">
        <tr><th>Parameter [Unit]</th><th>Value</th></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Mass Loss Rate [M<sub>⊙</sub>/yr]</strong></td><td>{{ mass_loss_rate }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Q̄</strong></td><td>{{ qbar }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>α</strong></td><td>{{ alpha }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Q<sub>0</sub></strong></td><td>{{ q0 }}</td></tr>
    </table>

    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us.</p>

    <p>Kind regards,</p>
    <p><strong>The LIME Team</strong></p>

    <p class="footer">Please DO NOT reply to this email.</p>
</body>
</html>

